&gt; &gt; That&#39;s my point - if this makes sense, I consider the semantics of
&gt; &gt; DELETE to be violated: The resource isn&#39;t deleted, its content is
&gt; &gt; being replaced with an empty representation. Hence my preference for
&gt; &gt; PUT.
