&gt; &gt; But admittedly the spec is pretty vague on this (&quot;The DELETE method
&gt; &gt; requests that the origin server delete the resource identified by the
&gt; &gt; request-target.&quot;). To me, this means that the resource should be GONE,
&gt; &gt; but YMMV.
